{"tid":1775894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"69到今日129，習慣了","createTime":"2019-12-09T06:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T08:42:47.000Z","uid":2719,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1d06b563a05c2e1805a165b2b0253a3440c671","tid":1775894,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"不知不覺就半年，時間快得令人驚訝，612、721、831仲好歷歷在目，完全唔覺得係幾個月之前嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經習慣咗抗爭模式嘅生活，就算黎多10個半年，都係一樣咁過，睇下邊個死先。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，即將迎接下一個半年，第二章節嘅開始主打經濟戰：（聖誕+新年）和理不消費同成立各行業之工會籌備香港首次真三罷，希望係來年嘅下半年，可以搞得成真三罷外，黃色經濟圈都逐漸蓬勃，再贏埋立法會選舉，為2021年打好基礎，重錘出擊！<br />\n<br />\n（唔相信抗爭可以係一兩年內贏到）"},{"pid":"e405205d498647514638a782c5f6f066f28527e6","tid":1775894,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e07b831be7b03ea08de48718f066910a6d164be","tid":1775894,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c317927e29e17dccc4a1f317c367d2df8ca152f8","tid":1775894,"uid":2719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e07b831be7b03ea08de48718f066910a6d164be","tid":1775894,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"期望工會有作為"},{"pid":"43cacda5f1485eb51f084654f5ad00834d9ab11e","tid":1775894,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"大家唔好忽略黎明甚至三罷嘅至勝關鍵 - 運輸界<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"522589a2740e39d59435e711035f9c4f91772774","tid":1775894,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"［改抗爭模式］想真罷工成功既請入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1de56fc16a62cf27fe8a9f